name: GLOBAL MUSIC FESTIVAL 004-A: PARIS:: CHAD XP'S BIRTHDAY CELEBRATION
description: This is the Global Music Festival: Paris Weekend 2, an experience in the Eight Meta's virtual 3D world with live original music by Ravin Dave + DJ Journey and NFTs by various artists in the community. This weekend, we celebrated an extraordinary NFT artist CHAD XP’s birthday. Find us on Instagram and Twitter @eightmeta @globalmusicxr
